<item>
            <title>[LU-13472] lnet: routing aliveness might be stale</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13472</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the case when the discover is toggled from on to off, the route aliveness might become stale due to not updating the route-&amp;gt;lr_alive variable correctly. It will get updated once the gateway is pinged, however, there is a period of max alive_router_check_interval where the route can be down.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
